cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as word and sentence similarity and part-of-speech tagging. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a simple approach for learning embeddings, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of nonlinear transformations for embedding could also suggest the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of convolutional neural networks, which could indicate the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
